This pattern of populating currentServers inside the other method, checkServer, after looping over all can be improved with something like:
  var children = context.getZooCache().getChildren(path);
  var liveTservers = children.map(TabletMetadata::checkServer).filter(Optional::isPresent).collect(Collectors.toSet());
  log(liveTservers);
  return liveTservers;
This requires checkServer to be modified to return either Optional.of(instance) or Optional.empty(), but I think it's more readable.

